{"serial": "00089", "department_serial": 4, "code": "LN1204", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Effective Workplace English Communication Skills", "ch": "高效職場英文溝通技巧"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "專業英文（ESP）中高級課程。 1.歡迎管理學院大二以上有修習EMI的學生選修課程 2.課程也 可以抵LN29課號，修課完成後請至語言中心辦理學分抵修。 3.第一次上課未出席，需事先跟老師請假，否則扣學期總成績 4.前兩週未出席者，老師有權退選該生。"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Liu, Chen-Yu"], "ch": ["劉貞妤"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["5", "6"]}, "loc": {"building": "TR", "room": "A205"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 30, "department": {"ch": "語言中心", "en": "Language Center"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 44, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "專業英文（ESP）中高級課程。 1.歡迎管理學院大二以上有修習EMI的學生選修課程 2.課程也 可以抵LN29課號，修課完成後請至語言中心辦理學分抵修。 3.第一次上課未出席，需事先跟老師請假，否則扣學期總成績 4.前兩週未出席者，老師有權退選該生。", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在協助學生培養有效職場溝通所需的基本技能。學生將學習撰寫清晰且專業的書面溝通內容，例如電子郵件和履歷表，並能根據專業情境進行調整。本課程還著重於提升口頭溝通能力，使學生能夠自信地參與會議、進行有效的簡報，以及專業地處理談判和電話交流。此外，學生將建立人際溝通技能，從而培養能與同事和客戶有效互動的全面能力。最後，本課程將鼓勵學生發展批判性思維、適應力，以及對文化差異的理解，為應對全球職場溝通挑戰做好準備。", "en": "This course aims to help students develop the essential skills needed for effective workplace communication. Students will learn to craft clear, professional written communication, such as emails and resumes, tailored to professional contexts. The course also focuses on enhancing verbal communication skills, enabling students to participate confidently in meetings, deliver compelling presentations, and handle negotiations and telephone conversations with professionalism. Additionally, students will build interpersonal communication skills crucial for socializing and networking in the workplace, fostering a well-rounded ability to engage with colleagues and clients. Finally, the course encourages critical thinking, adaptability, and an understanding of cultural nuances to prepare students for communication challenges in global workplace environments."}, "outline": {"ch": "第1周Orientation\n第2周Unit 1\n第3周Unit 2\n第4周Unit 3\n第5周Unit 4\n第6周Unit 5\n第7周Unit 6\n第8周Midterm\n第9周Unit 7\n第10周Unit 8\n第11周Unit 9\n第12周Unit 10\n第13周Unit 11\n第14周Unit 12; Peer-review session\n第15周Review\n第16周Final exam\n第17周Individual Consultation\n第18周Individual Consultation", "en": "Week 1Orientation\nWeek 2Unit 1\nWeek 3Unit 2\nWeek 4Unit 3\nWeek 5Unit 4\nWeek 6Unit 5\nWeek 7Unit 6\nWeek 8Midterm\nWeek 9Unit 7\nWeek 10Unit 8\nWeek 11Unit 9\nWeek 12Unit 10\nWeek 13Unit 11\nWeek 14Unit 12; Peer-review session\nWeek 15Review\nWeek 16Final exam\nWeek 17Individual Consultation\nWeek 18Individual Consultation"}, "textbook": {"ch": "Get Ready for International Business \nISBN：9786267239209", "en": "Get Ready for International Business \nISBN：9786267239209"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "10", "en": "10"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授", "en": ["Lecture"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "出席與課堂參與 20％\n簡歷影片與履歷 30％\n同儕互評 10％\n小組報告 20％\n期末考 20％", "en": "Attendance and participation 20％\nVideo CV ＆ Resume 30％\nGroup presentation 20％\nPeer review 10％\nFinal exam 20％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週一 9:00~12:00 或與教師預約", "en": "Monday 9:00~12:00, or by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "自學活動", "en": "Self-directed learning activities"}, "domain": {"ch": "應用英文", "en": "應用英文"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "語言溝通", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "文化視野", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "其他"]}, {"competencies": "自主學習", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "其他"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Language & Communication Skills", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance", "Portfolios Assessment", "Self Assessment/ P